      "start": 242.55,
      "end": 243.01,
      "text": "그러니까요."
    },
    {
      "start": 243.01,
      "end": 245.25,
      "text": "My mom told me not to tease my brothers."
    },
    {
      "start": 245.57,
      "end": 246.89,
      "text": "생활 속 단어였네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 246.89,
      "end": 249.35,
      "text": "약간 예고편 그런 느낌인가?"
    },
    {
      "start": 249.59,
      "end": 250.87,
      "text": "아, 티저."
    },
    {
      "start": 251.03,
      "end": 251.39,
      "text": "티저."
    },
    {
      "start": 251.59,
      "end": 252.63,
      "text": "아, 티저."
    },
    {
      "start": 253.19,
